
run Scala 2.11.7 in Netbeans 8.1, Ubuntu 14.04

commandline:
------------

check for java 
$ java -version
=> java version "1.8.0_60"

check for scala
$ scala -version
=> Scala code runner version 2.11.7


Netbeans:
---------

install Scala plugins:
Tools/Plugin and choose all Scala Plugins

restart Netbeans so that .scala files are not "unrecognized files".

create Scala project:
File/New Project/Maven/Project from Archetype/maven-archetype-scala-executable  

change Scala version in pom.xml (group-id org.scala-lang):
2.9.1 => 2.11.7

clean and build project

right click App.scala file and choose "Run File"

=> Hello World!

will be displayed

